    "body" : "<p>An alternative in Java 8:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] strings = list.stream().toArray(String[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Java 11+:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] strings = list.toArray(String[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 7721153,
      "reputation" : 780,
      "user_id" : 5847353,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-jfot8t8sHIk/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAWU/Zr9N_suIxD0/s256-rj/photo.jpg",
      "display_name" : "codecubed",
